#Control Statements – Syntax
1. if Statement
    if (condition) {
        // statements
    }
2. if-else Statement
    if (condition) {
        // statements
    } else {
        // statements
    }
3. else-if Ladder
    if (condition1) {
        // statements
    } else if (condition2) {
        // statements
    } else {
        // statements
    }
4. switch Statement
    switch(expression) {
        case value1:
            // statements
            break;
    
        case value2:
            // statements
            break;
    
        default:
        // statements
 }
5. for Loop
  for(initialization; condition; increment/decrement) {
      // statements
  }
6. while Loop
    while(condition) {
        // statements
    }
7. do-while Loop
    do {
        // statements
    } while(condition);
8. break Statement
    break;
9. continue Statement
    continue;


#Operators – Syntax
Arithmetic Operators
   a + b
   a - b
   a * b
   a / b
   a % b
Relational Operators
  a == b
  a != b
  a > b
  a < b
  a >= b
  a <= b
Logical Operators
  a && b
  a || b
  !a
Assignment Operators
  a = b;
  a += b;
  a -= b;
  a *= b;
  a /= b;
  a %= b;

Increment / Decrement
  a++;
  ++a;
  a--;
  --a;
Ternary Operator
  condition ? value1 : value2;

